Product Description: At Fatmug Designs, our prime focus is quality and convenience. Crafted with the water repellent diamond polyester fabric and sturdy hardware, FATMUG Foldable Duffel Bag 60L is a practical and multi-functional bag. This would be your go to companion for travelling as a weekender bag, spacious travel bag, emergency storage  bag, overnight bag, camping Duffle, Airplane cabin luggage, carry-on luggage and much more. The foldable quality makes it extremely easy to carry to be your ideal secondary storage as and when needed.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Lay your Fatmug Duffel Bag on a flat surface, with the front side facing down. Leave a slight opening on the main zipper and push out any excess air that may be inside the duffel bag.  Fold excess fabric towards the middle of the bag. Make sure that both the shoulder and handle straps are put inside in the middle of the bag, and are not flapping outside.  Fold the duffel bag from left to right, while ensuring all excess fabric and the handle stay inside the middle of the duffel bag.  Begin to zip up the duffel into its own self-containing pouch. Please zip it up slowly, so you will not accidently snag any loose fabric. It is recommended to use one hand to zip the pouch and the other hand to push any loose fabric into the bag that may possibly snag on the zipper.  --------------------------------------------------------------------  Fold it when you don't need it to save space  Easily folds to attain a 11 inch X 11 inch dimension to help you carry as a possible secondary storage as and when required  --------------------------------------------------------------------  Separate Shoes Compartment  Neatly stitched and thoughtfully designed shoes compartment to keep your main compartment clean and germs free while travelling  --------------------------------------------------------------------  Neatly Designed Travel Sleeve  Attaches nicely to your luggage suitcase and gives your shoulders the much needed break when you are heavily packed  --------------------------------------------------------------------  External Quick Access Pockets  Keep your frequently needed items in the neatly designed and user friendly external zippers  to avoid hassle of finding things in the main compartment                                                              Folded View                                                              Neatly designed Shoe Pocket                                                              Luggage sleeve                                                              External Pockets                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         Smooth durable zippers allow easy access to inside things without getting stuck and are built to last a lifetime  With sling, one length suits all is never the case. Product Description: Wondering how to handle the daily waste which is out there? Want to also segregate the different types of waste which is getting created so that it can be recycled properly? Wondering how the road side garbage bags are different than "G 1" Garbage bags ?  G 1 Garbage Bags are made up of Virgin Material, which does not smell bad when you open the packets. As it is made of Virgin Material it has all the tensile strength to hold your garbage without tearing off easily and you do not need to double the bags in the dustbin.  These comes in various colors like Black, Blue and Green to help you store different wastes separately for easy recycling of the garbage.   Multipurpose                                                                                                                                                                                          Black color Garbage bag is used to collect General Purpose wastes. General waste, also called residual waste, is material from businesses and households that cannot be recycled. It includes materials such as plastics, polythene, some packaging and kitchen scraps.  Green Color Garbage Bag is used to collect wet Waste. WET WASTE includes cooked and uncooked food, fruits, vegetable peels, flower waste, and other waste.  Blue Color Garbage Bag is used to collect Dry Waste. Dry waste is typically defined as any waste which will not rot or disintegrate over time and has little or no moisture content. Dry waste can also be described as inorganic waste given its lack of food products. Some common dry waste item are Metal, Glass, Plastic, paper, cardboard, aluminium foil, etc.,  Gusseted trash bag are sealed on the bottom and the sides are tucked in to form gussets, or extensions. Trash placed in a gusset sealed bags tend to spread to all areas of the bag, making this is a popular choice for many types of trash cans. Depositing wet trash and liquids should be avoided in a gusset sealed bag to avoid leaks. The widths of the gussets are often included in the total width of the bag. For example, a 14 inch wide bag, with 2.5 inch gussets on each side would be stated as 19 inches wide. Most of our low density liners have a gusset seal.                             MATERIAL
Description: Black coloured garbage bags with bottom sealing and prevents any leakage; Material: Semi virgin material, strong material to carry daily waste easily   Pack of 04 x 30 bags is equal to total 120 bags   Medium size (48 cm x 54 cm)   Most convenient method of garbage disposal to maintain cleanliness and hygiene

Product Description: Wondering how to handle the daily waste which is out there? Want to also segregate the different types of waste which is getting created so that it can be recycled properly? Wondering how the road side garbage bags are different than "G 1" Garbage bags ?  G 1 Garbage Bags are made up of Virgin Material, which does not smell bad when you open the packets. As it is made of Virgin Material it has all the tensile strength to hold your garbage without tearing off easily and you do not need to double the bags in the dustbin.  These comes in various colors like Black, Blue and Green to help you store different wastes separately for easy recycling of the garbage.   Multipurpose                                                                                                                                                                                          Black color Garbage bag is used to collect General Purpose wastes. General waste, also called residual waste, is material from businesses and households that cannot be recycled. It includes materials such as plastics, polythene, some packaging and kitchen scraps.  Green Color Garbage Bag is used to collect wet Waste. WET WASTE includes cooked and uncooked food, fruits, vegetable peels, flower waste, and other waste.  Blue Color Garbage Bag is used to collect Dry Waste. Dry waste is typically defined as any waste which will not rot or disintegrate over time and has little or no moisture content. Dry waste can also be described as inorganic waste given its lack of food products. Some common dry waste item are Metal, Glass, Plastic, paper, cardboard, aluminium foil, etc.,  Gusseted trash bag are sealed on the bottom and the sides are tucked in to form gussets, or extensions. Trash placed in a gusset sealed bags tend to spread to all areas of the bag, making this is a popular choice for many types of trash cans. Depositing wet trash and liquids should be avoided in a gusset sealed bag to avoid leaks. The widths of the gussets are often included in the total width of the bag. For example, a 14 inch wide bag, with 2.5 inch gussets on each side would be stated as 19 inches wide. Most of our low density liners have a gusset seal.                             MATERIAL
Description: Black coloured garbage bags with bottom sealing and prevents any leakage; Material: Semi virgin material, strong material to carry daily waste easily   Pack of 04 x 30 bags is equal to total 120 bags   Medium size (48 cm x 54 cm)   Most convenient method of garbage disposal to maintain cleanliness and hygiene
